<div id="review_1075487850" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1075487850" />
    <a title="Deborah" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4350507-deborah"><img alt="Deborah" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1285708989p2/4350507.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1075487850?book_show_action=true">Oct 08, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Deborah" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Deborah" href="/user/show/4350507-deborah">Deborah</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1075487850" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17491887896328776282">An exceptionally well written story, full of wit, great dialogue, and such memorable characters. Reminds us adults can be the worst bullies, but also true heroes. The author creates scenes where it really feels you&apos;re in the room with these interesting group of teens; I&apos;ll certainly look for more books by him. While the ending seemed a bit rushed and detoured a bit from the pace of the rest of the novel it is still highly recommended.</span>
  <span id="freeText17491887896328776282" style="display:none">An exceptionally well written story, full of wit, great dialogue, and such memorable characters. Reminds us adults can be the worst bullies, but also true heroes. The author creates scenes where it really feels you're in the room with these interesting group of teens; I'll certainly look for more books by him. While the ending seemed a bit rushed and detoured a bit from the pace of the rest of the novel it is still highly recommended.</span>
  <a data-text-id="17491887896328776282" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

